										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Germaine, an exquisite vintage porcelain doll from France, captures the essence of timeless elegance. Dressed in a delicate light blue gown adorned with intricate lace trim, she is a stunning representation of French craftsmanship. What makes Germaine truly unique is the use of a special firing technique known as “Lumière de Nuit,” a method developed by French artisans to achieve a soft, ethereal glow in the porcelain. Germaine is one of less than 50 known dolls made using this technique, making her a rare and highly sought-after collectible.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
